---
import { Plus} from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Get answers to common questions about as-built drawings and our professional documentation services
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              What are as-built drawings and why are they important?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            As-built drawings are accurate CAD documentation of buildings and systems as they were actually 
            constructed, including all changes and modifications from the original design. They're essential 
            for facility management, renovation planning, maintenance, and compliance requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              What building systems do you document in as-built drawings?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>We document all major building systems including architectural layouts, structural elements, 
            mechanical (HVAC), electrical, plumbing, fire protection, and specialty systems.</p>
            <p>Our comprehensive approach ensures complete facility documentation covering every aspect 
            of the built environment for effective management and future planning.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              How accurate are your field measurements and documentation?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our field surveys achieve Â±3mm accuracy using professional-grade laser measurement equipment 
            and total stations. We employ rigorous quality control processes including multi-point verification 
            and cross-referencing to ensure the highest level of accuracy in our documentation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              What CAD formats and standards do you follow?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We provide drawings in industry-standard formats including AutoCAD (.dwg), Revit (.rvt), and PDF. 
            Our layering and annotation follow AIA and National CAD Standards (NCS) conventions, ensuring 
            compatibility with existing design and facility management systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              How long does the as-built documentation process take?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>Typical projects follow a 3-4 week timeline: Week 1 for field survey and measurement, 
            Week 2 for CAD development and drafting, Week 3 for quality review and verification, 
            and Week 4 for final delivery.</p>
            <p>Timeline may vary based on project size and complexity. We provide detailed project 
            schedules and regular progress updates throughout the process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              Can you work with occupied buildings and minimize disruption?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we specialize in working within occupied facilities with minimal disruption to operations. 
            Our experienced surveyors coordinate with facility management to schedule work during optimal 
            times and use non-intrusive measurement techniques whenever possible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-8">
              Do you provide ongoing support and drawing updates?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-8 pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We provide comprehensive post-delivery support including drawing revisions, format conversions, 
            and updates for facility modifications. Our team maintains project files and can provide 
            ongoing documentation services as your facility evolves over time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-cyan-500 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Need Accurate As-built Documentation?</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">Our experts are ready to document your facility with precision and professionalism</p>
        <a href="/contact?#contact-form" class="bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300 inline-block">
          Start Your Project
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Add FAQ toggle functionality
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqButtons: NodeListOf<HTMLButtonElement> = document.querySelectorAll('section button');
    
    faqButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function(this: HTMLButtonElement) {
        const content = this.nextElementSibling as HTMLElement;
        const icon = this.querySelector('svg') as SVGSVGElement;
        
        if (content.style.display === 'none' || content.style.display === '') {
          content.style.display = 'block';
          icon.classList.remove('lucide-plus');
          icon.classList.add('lucide-minus');
        } else {
          content.style.display = 'none';
          icon.classList.remove('lucide-minus');
          icon.classList.add('lucide-plus');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>